name: Srikandi Panda - KuD-053
description: She is a princess from Panchala Kingdom. The story says that she is a reincarnated princess from past kingdom known as Kasi Kingdom. In her new life, she is raised as a man and a warrior. She grown as fine brave female warrior. She became person responsible for safety and security of her kingdom. She Participate on lots of wars to preserve peace in her kingdom.
